fallback_records_actual_mode — configure Lattice, create conflict, verify ResolutionRecord.actual_mode == LWW. E2E SCRIPT scripts/e2e_foundation_soundness.sh: (11) Fresh init, run full test suite, verify 0 failures. (12) Run braid status on empty store — no NaN in output. (13) Create observation with em-dash character — no panic. (14) Stress: 100 observations, verify F(S) is finite after each. FAILURE DIAGNOSTICS: Each test should log: (a) the exact assertion that failed, (b) the expected vs actual values, (c) the store state at failure (datom count, entity count), (d) for isomorphism test: per-component comparison table. ACCEPTANCE: (A) All 14 test specifications implemented. (B) All tests pass in CI. (C) E2E script exits 0. (D) Failure diagnostics produce actionable output when triggered."
